{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "a1b2c3d4-hosp-0001-gateway",
    "name": "Hospitality Platform — Gateway API",
    "description": "Calls the **gateway** only (inventory + reservations).\n\n**Setup:** import the example environment, set `baseUrl` and `access_token` (Auth0 access token with your API `aud` and claim **`https://hospitality.app/claims/enterprise_id`** — PLG demo: `eeeeeeee-eeee-4eee-8eee-eeeeeeeeeeee`). Staff also need a row in **`inventory.staff_member`** keyed by JWT **`sub`** (see **`docs/AUTHORIZATION.md`**). Run **GET List hotels** then **GET Room types** so **collection** variables `hotel_id` / `room_type_id` fill in.\n\n**Multi-brand (0017–0018):** optional **`chain_code`** collection var (e.g. **`HBR`**) — collection pre-request adds **`x-chain-code`** on every request when set. Public catalog: **GET List enterprises** / **GET Enterprise chains** (no auth). Authenticated: **GET My chains**, optional **`chain_id`** on **GET List reservations**. Managers: **01 — Admin staff** folder (**`staff:admin`**).\n\n**Phase 4 inventory:** **GET Search stays**, **GET Room type calendar**. Optional **`rate_plan_code`** / **`promotion_code`** (DEMO **LOS3**, **SAVE5**).\n\n**Phase 5:** soft holds (**0015**); **GET Reservation** saves **`reservation_etag`** for **`If-Match`** on **PATCH**.\n\n**Phase 6:** **`cancellation_reason`** on cancel; reservation notes (**0016**). Claim **`https://hospitality.app/claims/roles`**: `guest`, `front_desk`, `manager`, `read_only`, `integration`. Legacy tokens with **`chain_id`** only still work when **`enterprise_id`** is absent.\n\n**Variables:** environment overrides collection for the same name — example env only defines `baseUrl`, `access_token`, `check_in`, `check_out`.\n\n**Conventions:** folders by domain; Bearer on protected folders; **00 — Public** uses `noauth`. Reservation flow: **Create** → **GET** → **Guest** → **Notes** → **Confirm** → **Cancel**.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "https://hospitality-gateway.example.workers.dev"
    },
    {
      "key": "access_token",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "hotel_id",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "room_type_id",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "reservation_id",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "check_in",
      "value": "2026-06-01"
    },
    {
      "key": "check_out",
      "value": "2026-06-04"
    },
    {
      "key": "idempotency_key",
      "value": ""
    },
    {
      "key": "rate_plan_code",
      "value": "",
      "description": "Optional; e.g. DEMO **LOS3** (use with3+ nights). Empty = omit meaningfully in query/body."
    },
    {
      "key": "promotion_code",
      "value": "",
      "description": "Optional; e.g. DEMO **SAVE5**. Empty = BAR / no promo."
    },
    {
      "key": "search_hotel_ids",
      "value": "",
      "description": "Optional comma-separated hotel UUIDs for **GET Search stays**. Leave blank to search all hotels in the chain."
    },
    {
      "key": "calendar_from",
      "value": "2026-06-01",
      "description": "Half-open range start for **GET Room type calendar** (YYYY-MM-DD)."
    },
    {
      "key": "calendar_to",
      "value": "2026-07-01",
      "description": "Half-open range end (exclusive) for calendar."
    },
    {
      "key": "soft_hold_id",
      "value": "",
      "description": "Set by **POST Create soft hold** test script (migration **0015**)."
    },
    {
      "key": "reservation_etag",
      "value": "",
      "description": "Weak ETag from **GET Reservation** / **POST Create**; optional **If-Match** on PATCH (**FR-R11**)."
    },
    {
      "key": "cancellation_reason",
      "value": "guest_request",
      "description": "Optional on **PATCH Cancel**: guest_request | no_show | duplicate | rate_dispute | other (**FR-R9**)."
    },
    {
      "key": "chain_code",
      "value": "HBR",
      "description": "Active brand code; collection pre-request sends **x-chain-code** when non-empty. Clear for enterprise-wide staff calls."
    },
    {
      "key": "enterprise_code",
      "value": "PLG",
      "description": "Enterprise catalog code (Palladium Lodging Group demo)."
    },
    {
      "key": "chain_id",
      "value": "",
      "description": "Optional brand UUID filter on **GET List reservations**; **GET My chains** may set first chain id."
    },
    {
      "key": "staff_member_id",
      "value": "",
      "description": "Set by **POST Create staff member** or manually for admin PATCH/PUT."
    }
  ],
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "prerequest",
      "script": {
        "type": "text/javascript",
        "exec": [
          "function __t(v) {",
          "    if (v === undefined || v === null) return '';",
          "    return String(v).trim();",
          "}",
          "const cc = __t(pm.variables.get('chain_code'));",
          "if (cc) {",
          "    pm.request.headers.upsert({ key: 'x-chain-code', value: cc.toUpperCase() });",
          "}"
        ]
      }
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "00 — Public",
      "item": [
